<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
    
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
        {# Run `composer require symfony/webpack-encore-bundle`
           and uncomment the following Encore helpers to start using Symfony UX #}
        {% block stylesheets %}
     <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@500;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
     <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
     <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="style/main.css">
     <title>RAM</title>
        {% endblock %}
        {%  block header %}
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
  <div class="container-fluid">

    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-md-end" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
    {% if is_granted('IS_AUTHENTICATED_FULLY') %}
        <button type="button" alt="Disconnect" class="btn text-light me-2 mt-3"><a class="nav-link" style="text-decoration:none;color:white;" href="/logout" role="button">Log Out</a></button>
        {% else %}
    <button type="button" alt="connect" class="btn text-light me-2 mt-3"><a class="nav-link" style="text-decoration:none;color:white;" href="/login" role="button">Log In</a></button>
    <button type="button" alt="inscription" class="btn btn-outline-light me-2 mt-3"><a class="nav-link" style="text-decoration:none;color:white;" href="/register" role="button">Register</a></button>
    {% endif %}
  
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<header class="container mt-5">
 <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
    <h1 class="text-center">RANDOM ACCESS MOOD</h1>
    <p>Some days you will learn something, maybe from someone maybe from your experiences maybe from life. The concept is simple, share this positive attitude, this advice, this mood with us. just like a bottle in the sea, someone will read this.Are you in a bad mood ? it’s ok, no one forced you to be happy we all go through disappointment sometimes, share it too ! Maybe you’ll help someone to understand that there is always worse than we think and maybe their next card will be in the positive desk.</p>
    </div>
 </div>
</header>
        {% endblock %}

        {% block javascripts %}
           <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-JEW9xMcG8R+pH31jmWH6WWP0WintQrMb4s7ZOdauHnUtxwoG2vI5DkLtS3qm9Ekf" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
           <script src="js/main.js"></script>
        {% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>
        {% block body %}
        
        
        {% endblock %}
    </body>
</html>
